{
  "stem": "5388.7",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It's-- it's that-- kind of like in the-- like the story from Grodno.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "This is specific, local policeman watching a cemetery, dreaming about the gate.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There is no big philosophizing on the subject, you know?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And here, this little boy, he sees the injustice that goes on and the slaughter, and-- and he just says why, why, why?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The question is why.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And that song, the title is [SPEAKING YIDDISH]. 'Does it Has to be Like That?' Would you sing that?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sure.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think maybe I would do better if I read-- if I sing it straight from the Yiddish part of that part, OK?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[SINGING IN YIDDISH] That's basically it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[DRINKS] It did have a touch, in-- that song always did.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No question about it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No question about it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because the local stuff-- OK, ghetto, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But here is this philosophical-- the-- the-- the-- the question of is there essence of it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Why-- why should it be like that?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Who did it like that?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Who constructed such a thing?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[CRYING] And it's not merely just a question of gooder life, bad, good life, better life.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I mean, it's life and death.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[CRYING] The whys of injustice.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The why.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Absolutely.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SPEAKING GERMAN]",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That is-- yes, it's quite a song.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's-- I don't remember fully the word, but I know some of this part.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I just got it, too.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It is the song that's the steps.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The song goes, one, two, three, one, two, three-- the marching.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it talks about, you know, it's good when you know where you're going, for what and for why.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because here the people are marching, they're marching to the graves.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the question is asked, where is your-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] [SPEAKING GERMAN]",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's really the death march.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
